---
---

<section class="about-studio">
  <div class="container about-studio-inner">

    <img src="/barra-superior.svg" class="about-studio-bar-top" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />

    <div class="about-studio-left">
      <img src="/barra-lateral-vertical.svg" class="about-studio-bar" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />
      <div class="about-studio-left-text">
        <h2 class="about-studio-headline">
          Clareza e sensatez acima do hype
        </h2>
        <p class="about-studio-body">
          Nossa missão é desenvolver e implementar soluções com clareza e sensatez para os negócios.
          Não é metáfora. É o antídoto para dois males que a gente vê todo dia no mercado de
          tecnologia: projetos que ninguém entende e decisões tomadas no hype.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-studio-right">
      <div class="about-studio-item">
        <div class="about-studio-check">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="var(--laranja)"/>
            <path d="M5.5 10.5L8.5 13.5L14.5 7" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="about-studio-value">Não negociamos com a mediocridade.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-studio-item">
        <div class="about-studio-check">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="var(--laranja)"/>
            <path d="M5.5 10.5L8.5 13.5L14.5 7" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="about-studio-value">Liberdade com responsabilidade.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-studio-item">
        <div class="about-studio-check">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="var(--laranja)"/>
            <path d="M5.5 10.5L8.5 13.5L14.5 7" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="about-studio-value">Dividir para multiplicar.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-studio-item">
        <div class="about-studio-check">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="var(--laranja)"/>
            <path d="M5.5 10.5L8.5 13.5L14.5 7" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="about-studio-value">É melhor ter um cliente satisfeito do que vinte insatisfeitos.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-studio {
    background: #fff;
    padding: var(--space-9) 0;
  }

  .about-studio-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(48px, 6vw, 96px);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-studio-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .about-studio-bar-top {
    display: none;
    width: 157px;
    height: auto;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about-studio-bar {
    width: 12px;
    height: auto;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: block;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .about-studio-left-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .about-studio-headline {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 50px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #0A0A0A;
    text-wrap: unset;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .about-studio-body {
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    color: var(--cinza-600);
    line-height: var(--lh-body);
    max-width: 540px;
  }

  .about-studio-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .about-studio-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about-studio-check {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .about-studio-value {
    font-size: var(--fs-h4);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0A0A0A;
    line-height: var(--lh-tight);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-studio-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-studio-bar-top {
      display: block;
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
    .about-studio-bar { display: none; }
    .about-studio-left { gap: 0; }
    .about-studio-headline { margin-top: 0; }
  }
</style>
